title: Macbook pro 820-4924 suddenly stops work
message:

title: Macbook pro 820-4924 suddenly stops work
message:
Incorrect PPBUS_G3H voltage.
Did you check SMC_RESET_L?

Do you get amber light on Magsafe?
Are you using original 60/85W Magsafe 2 charger?
